        </button>

        <Title
            city="Zagreb"
            country="Croatia"
            name="Armin Imširević"
            email="armin.imsirevic@outlook.com"
            phone="+385 99 4744 841"
        />
        <div id="summary" class="mb-3">
        <SectionTitle title="Summary" />
        <div class="text-xs mt-1 mb-3 dark:text-white">
            Full Stack Engineer with <b>8+ years of experience</b> delivering scalable backend systems and frontend applications for enterprise platforms. Proven track record in leading technical delivery, modernizing legacy systems, and mentoring cross-functional teams. Skilled in .NET, Java (Spring Boot), Kotlin, React, Node.js, and cloud-native architectures with Kubernetes, SQL/SQL Server, Elasticsearch, and Kafka. Experienced in stakeholder communication, architectural decision-making, and problem-solving in Agile environments. Delivered features that increased platform revenue, reduced technical debt, and improved performance. Experienced in core banking and telecom infrastructure (CPaaS, SMS).        </div>
        <div id="employment" class="mb-3">
            <SectionTitle title="EMPLOYMENT" />
            <RowEntry
                companyName="Infobip"
                title="Senior Full Stack Software Engineer"
                timeSpan={{ start: "Feb. 2023", end: "Present" }}
                location="Zagreb, Croatia"
                typeOfEmployment="Hybrid"
