                        "Led design and delivery of <b>cloud-native microservices</b> using <b>Java (Spring Boot)</b>, <b>.NET</b>, <b>React</b>, <b>Kotlin</b>, and <b>Node.js</b>, deployed on <b>Kubernetes</b> for high-volume enterprise workloads.",
