                        "Mentored <b>5 engineers</b> through <b>pair programming</b>, <b>code reviews</b>, and <b>design sessions</b>, raising team delivery standards.",
                        "Delivered secure, high-volume client onboarding flows with <b>cross-functional teams</b>, driving a <b>~12% increase</b> in SMS traffic.",
                        "Integrated <b>unit and integration testing</b> into the CI/CD pipeline, reducing regression defects and improving release confidence.",
                        "Applied <b>Agile practices</b> (TDD, iterative delivery) to accelerate development cycles and maintain high code quality."
                    ]
                }
            />
            <RowEntry
                companyName="Infobip"
                title="Full Stack Software Engineer"
                timeSpan={{ start: "Jun. 2020", end: "Feb. 2023" }}
                location="Zagreb, Croatia"
                typeOfEmployment="Remote"
                descriptionList={
                    [
                        "Rebuilt legacy login and signup systems into <b>secure microservices</b>, improving onboarding speed, cutting auth-related bug reports by <b>~80%</b>, and reducing tech debt by <b>~65%</b>.",
                        "Delivered <b>Kafka to Elasticsearch</b> pipeline for high-volume audit logs, enabling real-time search, analytics, and compliance reporting at scale.",
                        "Contributed across multiple stacks (<b>.NET</b>, <b>Java</b>, <b>Node.js</b>, <b>React</b>) after rapid upskilling in <b>Kotlin</b> and <b>C#</b>, delivering production features across backend and frontend systems."
                    ]
                }
            />
            <RowEntry
                companyName="Oradian"
                title="React/Scala Software Engineer"
                timeSpan={{ start: "Sep. 2018", end: "Jun. 2020" }}
                typeOfEmployment="Remote"
                location="Zagreb, Croatia"
                descriptionList={[
                    "Developed <b>React</b> features integrated with <b>Scala</b> backend services for a core banking platform.",
                    "Provided <b>Scala</b> training to frontend engineers, improving cross-stack collaboration and delivery efficiency.",
                    "Collaborated with <b>cross-functional teams</b> to deliver production-grade UI features under tight deadlines."
                ]}
            />
            <RowEntry
                companyName="Oradian"
                title="Backend Software Engineer"
                timeSpan={{ start: "Jan. 2017", end: "Jun. 2020" }}
                typeOfEmployment="Remote"
                location="Zagreb, Croatia"
                descriptionList={[
                    "Built scalable <b>Scala</b> backend features for the core banking engine, including a revenue-driving capability that increased company revenue by <b>~8%</b>.",
